== 季度总结 ==
[[File:Seeking_valuables_in_the_wreckage,_Galveston,_Texas.jpg|thumb]]

8月27日，[[佛得角|佛得角]]以西较远处海域发展出热带气旋，拉开飓风季序幕。风暴的最强[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]达每小时230公里，最低[[气压|气压]]936[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.6[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下已属四级飓风标准，是全季最强风暴。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>这样的开局日期可谓异常之晚，1944至1996年间平均每个大西洋飓风季的第一场风暴是在7月11日形成<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/sns-hc-canedates-htmlstory.html | title = Average hurricane dates | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160805235312/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sns-hc-canedates-htmlstory.html | newspaper = [[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]] | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | archivedate = 2016-08-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。相比之下，卫星时代形成日期最晚的首场风暴则是1977年8月29日的[[飓风安妮塔|飓风安妮塔]]<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161111015219/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2009-06-30-hurricane-season_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2009-06-30-hurricane-season_N.htm | title = Hurricane season off to a typically slow start | author = Doyle Rice | date = 2009-06-30 | newspaper = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | archivedate = 2016-11-11 }}</ref>。从气候角度来看，9月是大西洋飓风季的活跃巅峰，1900年9月共形成三个热带气旋，其中两个强化成飓风。第三号飓风于9月23日消散后，大西洋盆地的热带天气活动一度陷入沉寂，直到近两周后才有第五号热带风暴于10月4日在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]附近生成，风暴之后转变成温带气旋，同时第六个热带气旋又于10月10日在[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]发展成型。全季最后一个气旋是在东加勒比海形成，经过[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]后于10月28日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]和[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]之间转变成温带气旋。<ref name="HURDAT" />

所有风暴中以人称“加尔维斯敦飓风”的第一号飓风影响最大。风暴潮将德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]大部分区域淹没，致死人数在6000至12000之间<ref>{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2008/US/weather/09/12/galveston.1900/ | title = Hurricane destroyed Galveston in 1900 | author = K.C. Wildmoon | date = 2008-09-12 | newspaper = CNN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081016022831/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/US/weather/09/12/galveston.1900/ | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | archivedate = 2008-10-16 }}</ref>。据正式渠道估算，整场飓风的死亡人数约为8000，截至2016年11月依然是美国历史上最致命的自然灾害<ref name="frank">{{cite report | author = Neil L. Frank | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.agu.org/pubs/booksales/hurricane/Chapter_05galveston.pdf | accessdate = 2009-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090325121125/http://www.agu.org/pubs/booksales/hurricane/Chapter_05galveston.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-25 | title = The Great Galveston Hurricane of 1900 | publisher = American Geophysical Union | pages = 129–130 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>。气旋当时还是有纪录以来致死人数第二多的大西洋飓风，仅次于在小安的列斯群岛夺走至少22000条人命的[[1780年大飓风|1780年大飓风]]。不过，[[1998年大西洋飓风季|1998年]]的[[飓风米奇|飓风米奇]]在[[中美洲|中美洲]]导致超过11000人遇难，超越加尔维斯敦飓风的纪录。<ref>{{cite report |url=https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/reports/mitch/mitch.html |title=Mitch: The Deadliest Atlantic Hurricane Since 1780 |date=2009-01-23 |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131224045502/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/reports/mitch/mitch.html |archivedate=2013-12-24 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-12-08 }}</ref>第一号飓风还在加拿大导致至少102人死亡，是该国历史上最致命的风暴之一<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161117191036/http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=En&n=CC8A7AA0-1 | url = http://ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=En&n=CC8A7AA0-1 | title = Notable Canadian Tropical Cyclones | date = 2012-01-30 | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | archivedate = 2016-11-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="GHCA">{{cite report | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=en&n=A386676E-1 | title = 1900-1 | date = 2009-11-20 | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | archivedate = 2016-11-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161120193311/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=A386676E-1 }}</ref>。除此以外，1900年大西洋飓风季的其他热带气旋基本没有造成破坏或人员丧生<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180950/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1900.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1900.pdf | title = Monthly Weather Review | author = Edward B. Garriott | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|United States Weather Bureau]] | pages = 375-276 | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>，只有第五号热带风暴的温带残留在加拿大夺走一条人命，并造成价值约十万美元的中等程度损失，其中大部分是铁轨受损<ref name="TS5CA">{{cite report | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-12-08 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=en&n=A57787B3-1 | title = 1900-5 | date = 2009-11-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161120193315/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=A57787B3-1 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-11-20 }}</ref>。

这年飓风季的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值为81<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>

